## Optional — Tear-down

Only run on explicit user request. Confirm first.

```bash
# Stop containers, keep volume
docker compose -f docker-compose.local.yml down

# Stop and wipe data (Postgres + Temporal schemas reset)
docker compose -f docker-compose.local.yml down -v
```

Never run `down -v` without explicit user confirmation.

